trans-unit.source: The NamedImagesCollection class represents a collection of <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage> objects, which are objects that have an associated image and a name that is unique to the collection.
trans-unit.target: NamedImagesCollection 类表示的集合<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage>对象，后者是具有关联的图像和到集合中唯一的名称的对象。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage>

trans-unit.source: This class is exposed as the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Images%2A> collection property of the root <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> object, and is only available at run time.
trans-unit.target: 此类公开为<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Images%2A>集合的根属性<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>对象，并在运行时才可用。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Images%2A>

trans-unit.source: An image can be any object derived from the .NET Framework <xref:System.Drawing.Image> class, such as <xref:System.Drawing.Bitmap>, which is created dynamically.
trans-unit.target: 图像可以是从.NET Framework 派生的任何对象<xref:System.Drawing.Image>类，如<xref:System.Drawing.Bitmap>，它在动态创建。</xref:System.Drawing.Bitmap> </xref:System.Drawing.Image>

trans-unit.source: The image can be stored in this collection, and then assigned at a later time to any image property in the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> control, such as <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.BackImage%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 镜像可以在此集合中存储，然后分配到任何映像属性中<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>的控制权，例如<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.BackImage%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.BackImage%2A></xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>稍后

trans-unit.source: When one of the image properties in the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> control is set by specifying a `string` value, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Images%2A> collection property, of type NamedImagesCollection, is first checked to see if an image with that name exists.
trans-unit.target: 当一个中的映像属性<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>控件设置通过指定`string`值，<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Images%2A>集合属性，类型 NamedImagesCollection，首先检查以查看是否存在具有该名称的映像。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Images%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>

trans-unit.source: If a matching <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage> object is found, this image is used.
trans-unit.target: 如果匹配<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage>对象找不到，使用此映像。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage>

trans-unit.source: If a matching <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage> object is not located, the string expression is treated as a URL, image resource name or pathname.
trans-unit.target: 如果匹配<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage>对象不是位于，字符串表达式会被视为 URL、 映像资源名称或者 pathname。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage>
